1
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,640
You guys...

2
00:00:59,079 --> 00:01:00,000
Do you know each other?

3
00:01:03,159 --> 00:01:03,880
No.

4
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:08,200
About what happened today...

5
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:10,079
Thank you.

6
00:01:10,879 --> 00:01:12,200
I didn't expect you and...

7
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:14,319
Lang Jiu to have such a deep grudge.

8
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:17,079
But the moment you appeared...

9
00:01:17,359 --> 00:01:18,719
You were so cool.

10
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:21,040
Truly the Ball King I've admired for ten years.

11
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:24,640
But why did you change your name?

12
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:28,159
And grew your hair so long.

13
00:01:28,439 --> 00:01:29,680
I didn't even recognize you.

14
00:01:30,439 --> 00:01:31,079
But...

15
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:34,000
The name Hei Ba sounds pretty good too.

16
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,480
You won back then with the Miracle Black Eight.

17
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:42,359
The competition back then...

18
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,239
Must have had a hidden story.

19
00:01:45,519 --> 00:01:46,719
We all believe in you.

20
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:48,959
How about...

21
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:52,280
How about you make a comeback?

22
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:53,879
I have many friends in clubs...

23
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:54,760
Who can help you.

24
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,480
With your skills...

25
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,640
You can definitely beat that pervert...

26
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,120
To a pulp.

27
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:01,760
I'm leaving now.

28
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,480
Why are you leaving?

29
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,560
I'm serious.

30
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,400
You don't think my skills are too poor, do you?

31
00:02:38,759 --> 00:02:39,960
Thank you for your trust.

32
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,319
Yesterday...

33
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:21,759
Lang Jiu's club was raided by the police.

34
00:03:22,159 --> 00:03:22,879
So satisfying.

35
00:03:23,439 --> 00:03:24,120
That kind of person...

36
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:26,080
Should be taught a lesson.

37
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:28,919
Did you take the wrong road?

38
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:30,080
Wrong road?

39
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:30,800
Where is this?

40
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,319
This...

41
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:04,240
No!

42
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:05,199
Help!

43
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:06,960
Help!

44
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:08,479
Wait a minute.

45
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,400
What's wrong?

46
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,120
Where is this?

47
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:30,519
It really is here.

48
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:33,399
Isn't this a tourist spot?

49
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,040
Why come here for an interview?

50
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,279
And confiscate phones too.

51
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:43,639
Seems it's not just...

52
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:44,959
As simple as selecting streamers.

53
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:47,279
Who's there?

54
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:48,680
Intruder!

55
00:04:48,839 --> 00:04:49,920
Evacuate all guests.

56
00:04:51,639 --> 00:04:52,319
Sorry, VIP.

57
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,160
Emergency situation.

58
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,360
We'll escort you out first.

59
00:04:58,439 --> 00:04:59,560
Ruining my fun.

60
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:04,560
Stop!

61
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,319
Don't run!

62
00:05:07,959 --> 00:05:09,079
Stop, don't run!

63
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,120
Stop! Stop!

64
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,439
Send a car to chase them, quick!

65
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,199
Why are you here?

66
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:29,160
Didn't you pull me up?

67
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,199
Aren't you supposed to be tough?

68
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:31,959
My idol is asking...

69
00:05:31,959 --> 00:05:33,279
Why are you being chased by security?

70
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,120
The more you know...

71
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,160
They're catching up!

72
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:37,759
Quick!

73
00:05:38,079 --> 00:05:39,000
Turn right at the speed bump ahead.

74
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:39,920
No.

75
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,720
We just went down that road.

76
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,759
It's a dead end.

77
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:43,519
Listen to me.

78
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:46,959
Turn right ahead and get in my car.

79
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,199
Stop all delivery vehicles nearby.

80
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,079
Someone broke in.

81
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:31,560
Seen enough?

82
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,120
Get out.

83
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,560
Idol.

84
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:42,759
Let's go.

85
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,079
What happened?

86
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,240
Have we met today?

87
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,319
Don't look at me like that.

88
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,079
I don't like stand-in romance...

89
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,319
Nor do I like interfering with couples.

90
00:06:57,519 --> 00:06:58,639
Take your sweetheart...

91
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,000
And stay away from me.

92
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,040
Go.

93
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:21,000
That was really close today.

94
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,519
Say,

95
00:07:23,439 --> 00:07:24,920
who were those people chasing us?

96
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,680
Gangsters.

97
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:29,959
But isn't Yi Xin the Madam?

98
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,199
Why didn't she

99
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,920
have her bodyguards take them out?

100
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:35,639
Or is it that

101
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,240
everything she did

102
00:07:42,439 --> 00:07:43,839
was all for you?

103
00:07:46,519 --> 00:07:47,000
Man,

104
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:49,759
you have successfully caught my attention.

105
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,920
Isn't that how it goes in TV dramas?

106
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:58,839
Or maybe

107
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:02,040
she is doing something dangerous.

108
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:04,240
What did you say?

109
00:08:06,439 --> 00:08:07,759
That's how it goes in TV dramas.

110
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:08,759
Not that line.

111
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,800
She is doing something dangerous.

112
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:14,839
Right.

113
00:08:16,399 --> 00:08:17,279
Where are you going?

114
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:26,480
Weiwei.

115
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,480
Are you doing something dangerous?

116
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,959
So you pushed me away on purpose?

117
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,759
Your phone keeps ringing.

118
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,720
Are you sure you won't answer it?

119
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,840
Could it be that everything back then wasn't an accident,

120
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,399
but there was a hidden story?

121
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:55,559
Who dares to break into Kaye Mountain?

122
00:08:55,919 --> 00:08:56,840
Go investigate.

123
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:57,440
Al-Al...

124
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,240
Already checked.

125
00:08:58,399 --> 00:08:59,200
It might be tourists.

126
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:00,519
It shouldn't be important.

127
00:09:01,799 --> 00:09:03,679
I decide if something is important or not.

128
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:05,200
Understood, Boss Nan.

129
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:06,240
I'll go right away.

130
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,039
Get Cheng Ye to make a comeback soon.

131
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,519
So the group can recover some funds.

132
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,039
Boss Nan, you are brilliant.

133
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,879
Release the news of Cheng Ye making a comeback.

134
00:09:14,279 --> 00:09:15,080
Those big bosses

135
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,799
will place bets on him.

136
00:09:16,879 --> 00:09:17,399
When the time comes,

137
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,759
we can...

138
00:09:19,039 --> 00:09:20,080
Only when he stands high enough

139
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:22,559
can we make him fall hard enough.

140
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,679
I didn't go looking for you,

141
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:45,840
yet you came knocking on my door yourself.
